# Copy this file to .env.local for per-machine overrides.
# Values here take priority over .env but are overridden by shell/CI environment variables.
# This file is gitignored - safe for personal secrets and machine-specific settings.
# Do NOT commit .env.local itself.

# -- JWT
# Override the JWT signing key with a personal/machine-specific secret.
# Must be at least 32 characters for HS256.
# Uncomment and set your own value:
# Jwt__SigningKey=my-personal-machine-signing-key-here!!

# -- Database
# Override the SQLite database path for local development.
# Uncomment to use a custom location:
# ConnectionStrings__Default=Data Source=/tmp/myapp-local.db
